\id JAS Matupi Chin Standard Bible 
\h JAMES 
\toc1 JAMES 
\toc2 James 
\toc3 Jas 
\mt1 JAMES CAPAT  
\mt2 (Letter from James)  
\imt1 JAMES CAPAT KAWNG  
\ip James capat he Jerusalem hlangboel mawtkung la aka James loh a tael. Anih he Jesuh kah a mana la om.  
\ip Baibal Olkhueh thai dongkah capat khuiah tah James capat bahoeng olpuei la om. Hekah capat Rom uknah ham khuila yilhcet coeng. Hnin takuem Khrihca khosaknah moeiboe kawng he yakming yoei la bawt a tael.  
\ip James loh canpueinah tah tangnah he khoboe rhoih pawt atah a phu om pawh. He nih hlang kah awt koila a om eh.  
\ip Anih loh poeknah mpaek he a caih la a thui, na khodaeng vaengah khaw ngaihmang sak boeh. Tangnah neh noemcai vaengah kobawt sak boeh. Thintoek ham loe sak boeh, khodaeng neh boei khaw hlaang boeh. Hlang ham a then sai lamtah na hmuilai neh huengaihnah khaw kuemsuem. Pathen kho kungah yalh tih Pathen cueihnah dongah ni hangdang ham a om. A thae te oel ham om. Na caeh long ah hoemdam boeh. Na boei akhaw khodaeng bomnah la om saeh.  
\ip James capat he AD 45-50 tluk vaengah a tael.  
\iot Sawt Yoeinah  
\io1 Kuttuknah \ior (1. 1)\ior*  
\io1 Tangnah cueihnah dongkah khosaknah \ior (1. 2-18)\ior*  
\io1 Pathen ol hnatunah neh olngainah \ior (1. 19-27)\ior*  
\io1 Boei kuirhang neh anaa khueh ngaih aih boeh \ior (2. 1-13)\ior*  
\io1 Tangnah neh bibinah \ior (2. 14-26)\ior*  
\io1 Cueihnah neh olcalthingka \ior (3. 1-18)\ior*  
\io1 Lunglai neh payalaiko \ior (4. 1—5. 6)\ior*  
\io1 Uehnah, rhennah, thangthuinah \ior (5. 7-20)\ior*  
